{"tid":2412091,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不如大家入嚟探下佢，問下佢點解咁容易就滿足，向佢請教下點樣搵單純嘅快樂","createTime":"2021-02-17T22:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T00:53:57.000Z","uid":165817,"like":190,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8d0fc433e40ff5f7a940193bac713897b705e2","tid":2412091,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T22:41:56.000Z","msg":"呢個人大家都好熟悉，佢就係15、20、25年前嘅自己。<br />\n<br />\n細個嗰陣，媽咪俾你星期五晚同啲同學仔msn到12點，都已經會當堂生猛哂，好開心好興奮咁講哂多謝媽咪。<br />\n<br />\n而家大咗，星期五晚碌連登碌到半夜三點，都仲係覺得好撚無聊，仲好似越碌越頹咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79GPML8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79GPML8.jpg&h=22c60afb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個嗰陣，搵到同台人send SMS固然好開心、甚至唔同台要俾一蚊都依然好開心，每次收到短訊都會開心得嚟帶點緊張。<br />\n<br />\n而家大咗，就算signal whatsapp俾你24小時免費任傾，但每次震機都完全冇以前嗰種興奮，甚至會覺得「唔好煩我啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D0s7yq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD0s7yq4.jpg&h=b45408c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個嗰陣，一個星期可能淨係星期二、四先有得睇追緊嗰套卡通片，仲要miss咗就唯有俾$40去碟鋪買返嗰集嘅DVD，但每個星期都等得好開心，去到播嗰下更加開心，播完第二日就返學同同學仔傾劇情。<br />\n<br />\n而家大咗，可能上google求其search，乜柒都已經有哂全輯俾你慢慢煲，但唔再係以前嗰種期待感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YMhO2jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYMhO2jf.jpg&h=fe63760c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個嗰陣，可能一星期得50蚊用，放學同幾個同學仔成身汗咁走入7-11買碗$5.0撈麵，已經覺得呢啲就係「享受」。<br />\n<br />\n而家大咗，有能力食餐豪啲，可能間唔中有餐已經俾得起一百碗撈麵，但都係覺得唔夠放學嗰碗撈麵咁有feel咁enjoy。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pX7Z8Zk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpX7Z8Zk.jpg&h=07210c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個嗰陣，老師一話播ETV，成班都起哂哄，因為終於可以hea少少咁上堂，聽到「一理通馬國明」仲開心過聽流行曲。<br />\n<br />\n而家大咗，雖然可能仲讀緊書，但就算阿sir播乜片都好、就算條片好睇過當年啲ETV幾十倍都好，都唔會提得起勁去睇，反而覺得係瞓覺好時機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEd26RW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEd26RW.jpg&h=bcfb9605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個嗰陣，聽到咩「腦肚眼頸」、「惠康聖誕大特賣」、「肥婆最緊要係脂肪」，已經可以玩幾分鐘，仲要忍笑扮成熟。<br />\n<br />\n而家大咗，好似好多笑話都唔再覺得gag咁，仲有啲會覺得幼稚。終於唔使再忍笑，反而仲要成日假笑扮小丑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DOq4EB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DOq4EB.jpg&h=81cccbd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個嗰陣，人生最大嘅煩惱就係pokemon個山窿同火箭兵團棟大廈，究竟點撚樣先出到去，覺得自己攬住隻100lv噴火龍喺度打山窿入面隻20lv小拳石，簡直係懷才不遇。<br />\n<br />\n而家大咗，終於出到山窿，成個世界俾你慢慢發掘，但先發現原來前路仲黑、仲難行過個山窿，而且原來有好多人係用金手指攞住隻500lv超夢夢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ryF1C7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FryF1C7u.jpg&h=8e09bddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n細個嗰陣，好多野都得來不易，一個短訊對答足足值兩蚊、一個星期睇得兩集卡通、一碗撈麵用咗一個星期10%使費。<br />\n<br />\n而家大咗，科技發達咗、資訊方便咗、搵錢能力強咗，當年搵到最多快樂嘅事物，而家輕鬆一百倍就可以搵多一百倍，其實supposed係比當年快樂一百倍先啱，但係覺得自己連當年百分之一嘅開心都冇。<br />\n<br />\n小朋友無憂無慮固然係主因，但自己越嚟越難滿足都係原因之一。試過睇返細個鍾意嘅卡通、玩返細個沉迷嘅game，音樂響嗰刻的確係有一剎那覺得返咗15、20年前，但好快就知道，就算啲音樂影像存檔全部停留喺15年前，但最重要嗰樣野 &mdash; 心態，幾努力都返唔到去。<br />\n<br />\n打完呢段野先發覺，喺我地以前未有任何能力嘅時候，其實原來已經有搵快樂嘅能力，只係自己唔察覺。大家加油唔好俾呢種能力繼續消失落去，自己都努力學習緊，共勉之啦唉~"},{"pid":"76edaf633f6f7dbc98f64d670bccbbd86b895d29","tid":2412091,"uid":6310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T22:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回不了頭了"},{"pid":"47ea1146496fc10478f68592831cd97509db013c","tid":2412091,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:04:50.000Z","msg":"無知是快樂，越了解世界點運作，人越頹"},{"pid":"aff9e3486f4480b5bd8fd4c4497c620daafb2f96","tid":2412091,"uid":131884,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:05:28.000Z","msg":"因為無責任要負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈大個 要負既責任就愈多"},{"pid":"4bcc8617811597071c72f157199a8e76074bccd2","tid":2412091,"uid":226466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:15:40.000Z","msg":"打online 驚識女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03bfc73edd4bfb54d3136a8971c72e700a238f8","tid":2412091,"uid":51540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d048e0cee2fedeee5c9bbe7a7c3cc4523c75492d","tid":2412091,"uid":329418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:53:53.000Z","msg":"或者細個嗰陣擁有嘅唔多<br />\n反而會更加識得珍惜每樣野都唔係必然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e92aaa76ca11924eb4df6e8655266fe386358e","tid":2412091,"uid":253494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:56:04.000Z","msg":"玩跑online識女仔 同係現實識唔到女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade5b4b78f9e8f5e953092cc1de66fb5aa697a89","tid":2412091,"uid":68375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:59:17.000Z","msg":"睇到好sad , but true <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8261ab3758d050666b02596008ce2e9689bb56","tid":2412091,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:16:24.000Z","msg":"人就係咁，<br />\n以前金幣朱古力我都收貨，金莎直頭係尊貴嘅象徵<br />\n而家唔係Godiva 級數我都唔會擺入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a87c9cc5271728842da5751ec823606565313f","tid":2412091,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ade5b4b78f9e8f5e953092cc1de66fb5aa697a89","tid":2412091,"uid":68375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:59:17.000Z","msg":"睇到好sad , but true <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />You're not alone bro"},{"pid":"f1d60cf69f70b1e441919029de7977edc5216fbc","tid":2412091,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41e92aaa76ca11924eb4df6e8655266fe386358e","tid":2412091,"uid":253494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:56:04.000Z","msg":"玩跑online識女仔 同係現實識唔到女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"記得細個icq求其打堆數字都可以識到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edfe10f943e6ece934bceeb2ea1fd1de9e72dd6","tid":2412091,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d048e0cee2fedeee5c9bbe7a7c3cc4523c75492d","tid":2412091,"uid":329418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:53:53.000Z","msg":"或者細個嗰陣擁有嘅唔多<br />\n反而會更加識得珍惜每樣野都唔係必然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"可能都有啲小朋友係咁<br />\n不過我自己細個嗰陣就冇諗咁多 或者唔識諗咁多<br />\n我細個嗰陣冇特別諗自己擁有多定少<br />\n淨係覺得咁樣已經好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d786321646f6dfa3696d71e5cea5f3c9942bb3de","tid":2412091,"uid":329418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5edfe10f943e6ece934bceeb2ea1fd1de9e72dd6","tid":2412091,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d048e0cee2fedeee5c9bbe7a7c3cc4523c75492d","tid":2412091,"uid":329418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:53:53.000Z","msg":"或者細個嗰陣擁有嘅唔多<br />\n反而會更加識得珍惜每樣野都唔係必然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"可能都有啲小朋友係咁<br />\n不過我自己細個嗰陣就冇諗咁多 或者唔識諗咁多<br />\n我細個嗰陣冇特別諗自己擁有多定少<br />\n淨係覺得咁樣已經好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"會因為擁有而好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者大個能力越大 可以擁有越多<br />\n反而無咗嗰種當係寶嘅感覺"},{"pid":"d22113a8da6c7993775a61b1049e05b4be3b4660","tid":2412091,"uid":244149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"因為簡單所以快樂"},{"pid":"9e9ddb44c4d40db4f9bc2a693d5893ce46027a9e","tid":2412091,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d22113a8da6c7993775a61b1049e05b4be3b4660","tid":2412091,"uid":244149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"因為簡單所以快樂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T22:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6f9f28c5b65ffc10842c55b89d6bcf9eb2d9f7","tid":2412091,"uid":85934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T22:49:31.000Z","msg":"細個冇錢打機買點數，但都會玩得好開心<br />\n大個咗終於有能力買好多點數，但已經冇咗打機嗰種心態，就算再玩返，都冇咗最初嗰種感覺"},{"pid":"b893e4d683a0ce013aed1833b53fc4b8a4880e4e","tid":2412091,"uid":273039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T22:50:54.000Z","msg":"學習過簡單、知足嘅生活"},{"pid":"e4008170b2013397856b343955d98f1367aba37e","tid":2412091,"uid":213980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T22:51:09.000Z","msg":"因為細個乜都唔洗你諗，只係食玩訓屌<br />\n依家大個就賺錢為左食玩訓同埋比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697fccdda19e50ee7b3bc09262f23e4a0f3bfc02","tid":2412091,"uid":336046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T22:59:23.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推 呢個post勾起咗好多我童年嘅回憶<br />\n其實我覺得做大人好開心 原因正正係樓主講嗰啲 最主要係自由 我有能力做到我想做嘅嘢 唔使再俾人管住 我而家鍾意食炸雞 我可以瘋狂地食 食到我唔想食 我可以買到我想要嘅嘢 唔使再日日早起身 有時好簡單 落街買杯雪糕已經好滿足 我細過未必可以 買完一袋袋餸 我覺得自己係一個大人又好得意 好多時行街我都會提醒下自己呢種大人嘅自由係幾好 其實我對自己都好好 返工咁辛苦 不如就對自己好啲去食壽司啦 咁我又好開心 呢種自由係我細個冇嘅 去到成年人 我先真正感受到咩叫對自己嘅人生負責<br />\n<br />\n我小學時已經好想有個女朋友，咁多年嚟都搵唔到，好對唔住童年嘅自己，我會努力㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b18884048646cc5484e7d3d21a2a0ddc391cb4","tid":2412091,"uid":336046,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:01:29.000Z","msg":"一篇好有心思圖文並茂嘅post 而家已經買少見少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc93bb8e96c741c66e854c619f4dbf6e2e970e27","tid":2412091,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:13:32.000Z","msg":"睇完篇文想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18276a8bd7a5805529af690253c8bb0d10c9c15","tid":2412091,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T23:34:21.000Z","msg":"人生識字憂患始"},{"pid":"63a078c99bba0b27850e39e17ef6a927d699765f","tid":2412091,"uid":40159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:17:41.000Z","msg":"歸根究底因為要返工"},{"pid":"04df2db7e14e9423511528167a10cf8132fd410c","tid":2412091,"uid":116976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:09:58.000Z","msg":"完全係本人寫照，細個最大既困難就係山洞同火箭兵團既基地。人大咗，搵到啲錢，但其實做奴工真係好空虛，亦唏噓，近期煩惱點樣搵番人生既愉悅感，睇完之後略有頓悟"}]}